                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870523-79-off366 t17870523-79-cd367"></join>, seven cloth coats, value 3 l. four cloth waistcoats, value 10 s. three pair of breeches, value 19 s. six pair of stockings, value 6 s. a cotton counterpane, value 2 s. and four shirts, value 10 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17870523-79-victim723" type="victimName">
